Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:08.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道结局会如何  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all know how this ends, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,全军覆没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,这应该算不上是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That shouldn't be a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以一个有着一生博学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what's an old, white man to do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,却注定要抹去的白人老头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a lifetime of knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,能做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}doomed to erasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,除了把它当做剑来使用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}except wield it like a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:30.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,伟人说放手一搏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great men say balls to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的团队尊重这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My crew respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  亲爱的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, dear family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,起床了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们距离出发已经过去了2468天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are 2,468 days from departure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:52.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,3天前和雪国列车重接在了一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and three days since reconnection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,献给一个特别的战友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For a special comrade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我选择了圣-桑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have chosen Camille Saint-Saens'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,《狮子皇家进行曲》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Royal March of the Lions."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:03.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是狮子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are lions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:06.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,前来从一群鬣狗手中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}here to reclaim our Engine Eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,夺回我们的永动机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from a gibbering pack of hyenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:13.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的自尊心悄悄靠近  等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our pride stalks, waits,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们每个人都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}each of you playing your part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,伟大远行中扮演着自己的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in a great odyssey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,有的人会比别人付出更高的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some pay a higher cost than others,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们中没有谁比冷淡鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and none among us have paid more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:25.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,付出的代价更大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}than Icy Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:29.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都应该像鲍勃一样做出牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We should all make sacrifices like our Bob,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:32.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,磨炼我们的意图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}honing our purpose to the ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的冷冻人团结我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let our Coldman unite us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的矛尖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the point of our spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我们重新夺回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the day we retake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,属于我的东西的那天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,末日其实并没那么糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apocalypse isn't so bad, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能勉强蒙混过关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you can just muddle through,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,展示出一点独创性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}show a little ingenuity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们就会为了城里唯一的演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}people line up for tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,而排成长龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the only show in town--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车车上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}aboard Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:26.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:30.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All 1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:50.75,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:50.75,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第三{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"浩瀚长征{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,面对怀疑  快速站立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Standing fast, in the face of doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是自己的怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}especially your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,-领袖必须这么做  -我知道  可是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's what a leader has to do. - Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,不该是一个母亲该做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's not what a mother should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果大地母亲要复活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Mother Earth is coming back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么是的  母亲应该这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then yes, it's what a mother should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,再过大约一小时  我们就要换轨道  驶向西边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About an hour left until we switch track and head west.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,早餐好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breakfast is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,让雪国列车开过那座山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's going to be a shit show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,会异常艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}getting Snowpiercer over that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们能闻到我们的鸡蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They smell our eggs, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们比从前更渴望新鲜事物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now they're craving fresh food like never before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:04.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,人人都得保持饥饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone needs to stay hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,伤疤可以提醒你你愿意付出多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hmm, a scar to remind you how far you're willing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,它只提醒了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All it does is remind me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮试图背叛我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that Melanie flipped the tables on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:17.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,可靠科学  地球可能会回暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sound science that the Earth may be warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,而她即将踏上一次真正的自杀任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she's departing on a veritable suicide mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,把我们可怕的革命者莱顿先生抛在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}leaving Mr. Layton, our fearsome revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我好激动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm tingling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会比割开他的喉咙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This will be far more fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,有意思得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}than simply slitting his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝  收到吗  这里是雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice, do you copy? This is Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,终于听到你们的声音真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's lovely to finally hear your voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是落基山脉旧测试轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the old Rocky Mountain Test Track.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,别名碎颈轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}AKA Neckbreaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我向你保证  比听上去危险得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I assure you, it's much more dangerous than it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个高点是我们能开到距离研究站最近的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This high point here is as close as we can get to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  雪国列车才是问题所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, Snowpiercer is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚开过碎颈轨道  那条轨道没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We just came over Neckbreaker. That track is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,但因为雪国列车必须为伯绍德曲线降速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But because Snowpiercer has to slow for the Berthoud Curve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们将没有足够的速度爬上山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we won't have enough speed to get up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,但一旦我们通过曲线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But once we're through the curve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝就可以激活我们的助推器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice can activate our booster,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我们足够的转力  让我们开过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can give us just enough torque to take us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,-没错  -如果不成呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's correct. - And if it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果不成呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"If it doesn't work?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗  莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that you, Mr. Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么跟工程师们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever are you doing among the Engineers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,平民监督  威尔福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Civilian oversight, Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是现在我们这的规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's how it goes up here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果不成功会发生这些情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens if it doesn't work is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须倒车离开那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we have to reverse out of there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,环绕世界一圈  再从另一个方向过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}go around the world, and come at it from the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不希望那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, we don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮会错失逃生的时机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie will miss her window to jump ship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,为拯救世界而牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and die saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,对吗  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Won't you, Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  我们会错过这机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we would miss this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是我们没有那么多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the truth is we don't have the luxury of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  那就是计划  我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so that's the plan. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝会送一份物资清单给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth is sending you a list of supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正确的静止列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't the right stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:58.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我和本上车拉设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would like permission to come aboard with Ben to pull equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,本不能上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope. Not Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  为什么本不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, really? And why not Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为大爱丽丝是禁本区  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because Big Alice is a Ben-Free Zone, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,那艾莉克斯可以帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then Alex can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  把清单送过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very well. Send me your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在边境等你  亲自搜你身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll meet you at the border and frisk you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们抵达落基山脉之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we have a thousand kilometers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一千公里废弃直线轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of dead straight track before the Rockies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们看看两个火车头能做成什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's see what two engines can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊  冲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vamos, vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开主轨道了  正开往落基山脉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've left the main track. Heading for the Rockies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德会借这些物资压榨我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Wilford's gonna squeeze us for these supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们仍需要零件维护雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we still need parts for Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有个主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I got an idea for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一起去边境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna come with you up to the border.
