Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  露丝  -谢我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thank you, Ruth. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,害我们要去落基山脉执行自杀任务吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Helping drag us into the Rockies on a suicide mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还是留给你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,她没让你好过  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She doesn't make it easy on you, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的建议是别骗她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My advice? Don't lie to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我后悔骗过她  而且我可能没机会补救了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I regret that I did, and I'll probably never make it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,但对你来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能留住她  她是少见的正直之人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she's a rare straight arrow if you can keep her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,请让开  罗切先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make way, Mr. Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你最好去边境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And best make your way to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:16.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,工程师和山脉  几乎和他们的自负一样大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engineers and mountains, almost as big as their egos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,下雪时我们会到达哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where will we land when the snow settles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿是和我妻子在卧铺上  手里拿着冰啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hopefully on a couchette, with my wife and a cold beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不是你的老大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not your boss anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里睡觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sleep in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,单身生活  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Single life, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和我的二等厢房间分手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I broke up with my Second Class cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是列车警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're Train Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿应该能帮你找个卧铺吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton should be able to find you a berth, for Pete's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我有更重要的问题要解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, I got more important issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么  那起车尾人袭击吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What? That Tailie assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:55.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,情况不妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,边境有大麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, there's much ado about something at the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so let's go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,橡胶印章  你看她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rubber stamps. I mean, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在车尾人要怎么运大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's a Tailie supposed to move a little weed now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,会成功的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能会成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就想引他的人上钩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want to set the hook in his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  这是进步的铃声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, the bell of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,边境有电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A hotline at the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,两辆火车能通讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and communication between the engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家现在都规矩点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's all be on our best now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是雪国列车乘客服务部的主管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Snowpiercer's Head of Hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备好过境了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are clear for crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:48.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事不是应该凯文来做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shouldn't Kevin be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我来  -可怜的凯文病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm doing it. - Poor Kevin is ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,一定是在你那边染上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Must have picked up something unsanitary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,不卫生的东西  莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over there with you, Mr. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看过你友敌的购物清单了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you seen your frenemy's shopping list?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,看了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir. I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想要六个氧化还原流电池  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want six redox flow batteries, Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,-艾莉克斯呢  -她在帮你准备降落伞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where's Alex? - Oh, she's packing your chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你紧张吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我可以给你四块  -不行  六块我都要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You can have four. - No, I need all six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样我才能熬过最开始的24小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I can make it through the first 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,并重新启动研究站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and get the station powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能给你一个高压雪橇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm not giving you a volt sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定你有三个高压雪橇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pretty sure you have three volt sleds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我有三个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I have three volt sleds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我给你一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but if I give you one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就只剩两个了  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll only have two, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实先生  那只是梅兰妮的清单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Actually, sir, that's just Melanie's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知雪国列车需要零件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer is in need of parts, as I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}particularly the, um--the--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,-转向架引擎  -转向架引擎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Bogie motors. - Bogie motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听说是三个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three, I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,那些很重要  鉴于我们现在都在同一列车上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're pretty important, seeing as we're all one train now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想我们或许能做个交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I thought that maybe we could work out a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,一些新鲜水果  蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some fresh fruit, vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,面包  鸡蛋  一瓶苹果酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bread, eggs, a jug of apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们每周给你们供应一次食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We will supplement your diet once a week
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,以此交换零件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in exchange for parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎是个能干的领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You seem like a capable leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很意外你在这么短时间内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amazing what you've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,长进了这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要在14小时后用高压雪橇  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm leaving on a volt sled in 14 hours, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,请求上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Permission to board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,乘客服务部很乐意护送  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hospitality will be happy to escort, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾  今天不行  露丝  会轮到你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Regretfully, not today, Ruth. You'll get your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,带她过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bring her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,再会  莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Adieu, Mr. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,很快  就只有你和他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pretty soon, it's just you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,27节补给列车  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}27 cars of supplies, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,27节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}27.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有的零件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the bits and bobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,生命的原料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The stuff of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,生存的希望大大提升了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the chances of survival just got a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,变暖趋势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A warming trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是天才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我整晚没睡  想着你的假设\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was up all night mulling your hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,这很合理  海德伍德夫妇同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's plausible. The Headwoods agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就下定决心去做  因为如果我们能改变气候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then put your mind to it 'cause if we can model it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那或许我们就能建立第一个殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then maybe we can build our first colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,放心  我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, I'm aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:34.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,厉害  你让整列车充满了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bravo, you filled the train with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:38.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,只可惜你要为数据而冻死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just sad you're gonna freeze to death for data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你也觉得这既悲伤又滑稽吗  艾莉克斯  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You find that tragic-comic, too, Alex? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会  只有要六块液流电池  她就会没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, with six RFBs, she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,那太可惜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,前提是你能到达研究站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you can make it to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  那是第一个难关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that's the, um, first hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧  达布斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can go, Dubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会陷入深厚  漂移的雪中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll be in deep, drifted snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:13.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要绕过任何裂缝或雪崩残骸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you have to detour through any crevasses or avalanche debris,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的雪橇就可能在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}your sled could be out of fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,到达研究站时耗尽能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by the time you get to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪橇可以没有能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the sled can stay dead
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到我必须回到轨道再说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until I have to get back to the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  因为我们不知道他们的太阳能板退化了多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, because we don't know how degraded their solar panels are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的数据系统需要一个可靠的能量源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and your data systems need a reliable power source
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,才能建立气候类型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to create a climate model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会搞定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,把电压表给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pass me that volt meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还没在爱丽丝上看见其他孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't seen any other kids on Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我是最年轻的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that would be 'cause I'm the youngest crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得接下去几小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just what do you think is going to happen here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over the next few hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,-越多越好  -挺讽刺的  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- As much as possible. - Kind of ironic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们在这帮你收拾东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause we're here packing your shit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,只为了让你再次离开我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that you can leave me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这比讽刺更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's worse than ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,令人心碎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你离开一次  那是决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You leave once, that's a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后你离开我两次  那就变成了选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then, you leave me twice, and then that becomes a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  我选择离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I'm choosing to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,但只是因为如果我不走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but only because there's not much chance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的未来就没有盼头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of a world for you if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you love to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁帮你打的耳洞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who pierced your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you ever laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去看看我睡觉的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll show you where I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,她不想迈尔斯看到她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She doesn't want Miles to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,她什么都知道  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She knows everything, mi hijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起  乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so sorry, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起什么  跟扎拉重新好上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For what? Falling back into Zarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我之前都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是你没死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, but you're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你活生生地在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,看着我  莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at me, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你孩子的母亲是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care who the mother of your child is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是谁对我下的毒手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know who did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:25.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不结盟  这是唯一的出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to make the alliance. It was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了她的计划  你牺牲了35名车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sacrificed 35 Tailies to her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说服他们参加抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The people that I convinced to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想和他们一起死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to die with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,而现在我们完全没有实现对他们的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now you've given them nothing that we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的领导能力也有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And your leadership is in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔茜  这个任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Josie, this mission--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,是梅兰妮的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Melanie's mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我相信工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I believe the Engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信这是我们最好的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe that this is our best chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我有义务保护它不受到威尔福德先生的破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and now it is my job to defend it from Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:57.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,革命分子无法成为优秀的政治家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Revolutionaries make terrible politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在就是这么看你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's how they see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还是车尾人  乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am still a Tailie, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:09.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你需要我的支持  不然你就会失去人心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you need my support, or you'll lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是没有大麻吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Still no marijuana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你出卖了自己是走私犯的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sold yourself as a smuggler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我走私我自豪  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I smuggle smugly, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚从边境来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just came from the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有机会参与一些高层贸易谈判的会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where I was privy to some high-level trade talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次我的建议是收下橄榄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My advice at this time would be have another olive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅长耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not my strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,那如果你没有大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if you got no weed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:41.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真不想你坐在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really don't want you sitting up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,别见怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是这样看起来不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It just looks bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟车尾人做生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, dealing with the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  莱茨  你得给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, Lights. You gotta show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,看到没  你觉得这看起来像什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See? What's that look like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定有看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You must've seen something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们用头套罩住了我  就在几秒钟之内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They blackbagged me. It happened in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看到他们跑掉了  他们戴着面具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw them run away. They had masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,把手指一起带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, took the fingers with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,传闻说是维修队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Track talk says it was the Breachmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也不会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not saying nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们只会更暴力地对待我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll just come gunning for me harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,她想要在集市里开一个维修铺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was trying to open a repair stall in the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:21.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果大家对我们仍有偏见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How free's a Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,车尾人怎么算是自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if everyone's still prejudiced against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,车尾一心  我们会保护自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, one Tail, all right? We'll protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道如何相互保护  防守阵线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all know how to protect each other and hold the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要越界  交给我们就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just don't cross it. We got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,有我支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会查清楚是谁干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna find out who did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会再来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they're not coming back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我之前说过了  威尔福德的人已经到这边了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I said it before-- Wilford's already got people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,维修队的人很喜欢威尔福德  讨厌车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, the Breachmen love Wilford and hate Tailies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是那证明不了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that's not proof of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人想把上帝的恐惧灌输给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone's trying to throw the fear of God into us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们就在名单的首位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they're top of the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗切  你要不要和她一起去找维修队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roche, you wanna go with her to visit the Breachmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不太想  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not really, no. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌维修队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breachmen. I hate these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以前是警察  所以像我那样做就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I used to be police, so just do what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做  把他们当成消防员来对待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that? Think of them as firemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样闯进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't just chip in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  波吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to see you, too, Boki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,不至于不至于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但我们这次是来登门拜访他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, but we're paying him the courtesy of a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,最近谁有戴面具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So who's been wearing masks lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,去茶室袭击车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Attacking Tailies up by the Tea Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,放下砝码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weights down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,维修队太过听从威尔福德的话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This Guild drinks an awful lot of Wilford Kool-Aid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们很多人都很高兴他回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of us are glad that he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:45.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,对于砍人手指的事你们有什么要说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, what do you gotta say about cutting off people's fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以边上油边说话  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, you boys can oil up and talk at the same time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛那么紧张  提尔警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why so tense, Detective Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们的人看上去比我壮得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys seem a lot more jacked than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我们在这榨取世界上最后的类固醇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we're juicing the world's last steroids up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也算是半个名人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are half-ass famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个引领了革命的司闸员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Brakemen helped lead the revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,正是我  你的人那个时候在哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's me. Where was your Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在这  我们当时在哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right here. We were in mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  当时我们发现威尔福德甚至不在火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, when we found out Wilford wasn't even in the Engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这对我们是极大的创伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was...very traumatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我们对革命置身事外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so we sat it out,
