Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你自己看着办吧  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're on your own, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,这你不用担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry about that.
