Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这床不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a nice bunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以装饰它们  但是这些床都差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We get to decorate them, but they're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,除了威尔福德的床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Except for Wilford's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把这装饰的很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you made it nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我用这个来形象化我们的路线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I use this to visualize our route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  同样的技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, um--me too. Same trick.
