Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后  到达这个最高点时  你必须出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then, at the highest peak, you have to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,乘坐雪橇一路回到研究站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and take the sled all the way back to the station.
