Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,低入西伯利亚  中国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}down into Siberia, China,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,高至喜马拉雅山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}up into the Himalaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们还要在一个月内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then we have to circle back to the station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,重回站点接你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and pick you up in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可真疯狂啊  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is some crazy shit, Mom.
