Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,她会告诉你她的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She lets you know how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车已经进入了前方的山脉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer's already in the mountains up ahead.
