Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,最好去检查下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better check.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:39.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to go.
