Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你和威尔福德面对面达成协定了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You cut that deal face-to-face with Wilford?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,建立交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Established trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,还没有  不过他会同意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not done yet, but he'll go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:52.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我担心的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That must be what worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:54.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个爱嫉妒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a jealous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:58.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,当他选择你的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, when he chooses you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:00.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就进入了他的场地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you enter his court.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,一开始很棒  他是个很棒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing at first. He's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:06.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后刀锋就暴露出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then the knives come out.
