Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮和我不允许他这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie and I refused to let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:13.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么大爱丽丝是一个"禁本区"吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that why Big Alice is a Ben-Free Zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:14.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:18.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,他嫉妒的不是普通的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His brand of jealousy isn't about anything normal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,像爱  背叛或是性爱的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like love or betrayal or sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,是关于控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just about control.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:27.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们或许要找个方法利用这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We might have to find a way to use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:29.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we might,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:32.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们还得和他一起穿过大半个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we still have to go halfway across the world with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以不论你有什么计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so whatever your plans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,不保留秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会一起回到梅兰妮那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll get back to Melanie together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:47.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我哥们怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's my boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:51.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,零下71度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}96 below.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:53.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,54分钟  历史最高纪录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}54 minutes. Best he's ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:24:01.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还需要再降温  时间也要更长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He needs to go colder. Longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:04.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有几个疗法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we have a few more treatments.
