Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:47.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,她还在那么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is she still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.40,0:24:51.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说有个车轮错位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said there's a wheel out of alignment.
