Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:56.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我问了驾驶的人  她是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I asked the Drive Train guys, and she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:59.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,第9节车厢  前负重轮  左后轮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Car 9, front bogie, left rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.74,0:25:02.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在兵舍下  我们都没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right under the barracks, and none of us even saw it.
