Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.04,0:25:10.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们想要她下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We want her off this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:13.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:17.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要听你说出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.94,0:25:19.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们想要她下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We want her off this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:25.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  我们在下坡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alice, we are on descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.60,0:25:28.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:32.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为你的盛大退场穿上毛线衫了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you got your woolies on for your grand exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.61,0:25:35.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,还没  但你就快除掉我了  乔瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, not yet, but you're nearly rid of me, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.65,0:25:38.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么本着这样的合作精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, well, in that spirit of cooperation,
