Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.28,0:25:42.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it's only fitting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.33,0:25:45.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,她开车送她妈妈进入来世最合适  你们说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she drive her mother into the great beyond, don't the rest of you?
