Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.16,0:26:24.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,-让所有人去集合点  -你能做到  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To get everyone to muster? - You can do this, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:25.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you can.
