Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:42.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,这值得再三强调\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it bears repeating...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.25,0:34:46.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,旅程永无止境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The journey never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.55,0:34:51.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望是真的  乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The hope is real, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.17,0:34:54.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮要下车去证明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie's getting off the train to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.30,0:34:55.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.72,0:34:59.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我皮肤冻住的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}While my skin was freezing over,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.60,0:35:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我蜷缩起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I curled up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.52,0:35:05.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,保住这只手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and protected this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.44,0:35:09.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我只需要一个拳头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause one fist is all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.29,0:35:24.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要当爹了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're going to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.95,0:35:28.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:32.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们所有人的指明灯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a guiding light for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.34,0:35:37.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果梅兰妮的任务是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if Melanie's mission is our only hope
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.59,0:35:39.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们下车的唯一希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to ever get off this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.64,0:35:42.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的人现在就有了一个新的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then our people have a new cause now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.41,0:36:46.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.91,0:36:49.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去准备过境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll go and prepare the crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.62,0:36:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.75,0:36:57.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我想你知道你的重心是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I--I think you know what your priorities are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.13,0:37:00.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我给你说一遍  看看我记住没有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, you want me to run it by you to see if I got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-保护科学  -这是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Protect the science. - Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.55,0:37:04.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,要做到这个  我得抵挡住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, to do that, I'll have to hold off
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.26,0:37:06.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,创造了这个世界的夸大狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the megalomaniac who created this world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.35,0:37:08.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还想要重新夺回权力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and wants to get power back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.06,0:37:10.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他已经有了一些支持者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he's already got some supporters on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.06,0:37:13.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会更多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that's about the size of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.52,0:37:15.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这让我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which leads me to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.07,0:37:17.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,他或许一开始就不想要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that maybe he didn't want anybody to get off this train
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:19.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,下车  重新移民地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and recolonize the Earth in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:22.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just so we're clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.99,0:37:26.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次任务成功与否看的是数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the success of this mission will be measured in data,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.66,0:37:29.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,而不是我的存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not my survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:34.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good luck, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.67,0:37:36.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good luck, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.85,0:37:47.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,派克  你可以出来了  我看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pike, you can come on out. I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.85,0:37:52.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,被你抓到我大便了  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aw, you caught me on the shitter, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.52,0:37:55.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我想要你再次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, I want you to link back up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.77,0:37:57.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟另一辆车的人脉联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with your connect in the other train.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.19,0:37:58.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你一条运输路线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm giving you a pipeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.28,0:38:01.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,-认真的吗  -但只能运大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're serious? - But only weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.24,0:38:04.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且我指定你能运什么过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I get to tell you what goes the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.33,0:38:07.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't let you down, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.50,0:38:15.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以信任莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can trust Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.09,0:38:18.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.09,0:38:20.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,他公正\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.55,0:38:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.72,0:38:25.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,好男人和好女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, good men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.68,0:38:28.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这里似乎很难保持善良  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't seem to stay good long doing this, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.73,0:38:34.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,答应我你会照顾艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please promise me you'll look after Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.19,0:38:38.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.61,0:38:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanna know someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.82,0:38:42.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,陪着她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.03,0:38:46.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是你的话  那对我会很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would mean a lot to me if it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.41,0:38:50.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我当然会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.41,0:38:53.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我答应你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:57.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.09,0:39:07.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:09.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备过境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are ready to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.73,0:39:18.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:32.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.54,0:39:38.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在你回来的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll all be waiting for you right here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.16,0:39:40.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:12.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,到达后立刻给防护服充电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you'll recharge the suit immediately upon arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.82,0:40:16.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,评估损伤  给庇护所打底漆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Assess the damage. Prime the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.74,0:40:18.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我担心的就是损伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the damage is what I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:22.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会在那即兴发挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll find things to improvise with there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.25,0:40:23.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.25,0:40:30.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他故意给你施加压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know he put that pressure on you on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.42,0:40:33.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,当他让你驾驶列车的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When he made you drive the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.97,0:40:36.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,当他命令你和雪国列车断开的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when he ordered you to disconnect Snowpiercer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.26,0:40:39.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,只因他想要你的良心背负着那些死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just 'cause he wanted all that death on your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.14,0:40:42.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want you to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.94,0:40:45.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的残忍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's his cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.77,0:40:48.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.07,0:40:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远别忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.03,0:40:55.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你再多留一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to keep you here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.67,0:41:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很想要踩刹车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to hit the brakes so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们做了我们必须做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we did what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.85,0:41:22.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是你所想的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, we're not who you think over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.68,0:41:25.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你有什么需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so if you ever need anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:27.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,这边有你可以信任的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there are people you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:34.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you, Allie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.45,0:41:41.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个月后见  妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll see you in a month, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.99,0:42:24.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,闪光信号就是下车点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Flare marks the drop point.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.41,0:42:25.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, guys. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.33,0:42:30.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,三秒后发射  三  二  一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fire in three, two, one.
